-----------------------------------
SURF_DROWNING_SUNLIGHT BY SILVERLOL
-----------------------------------

surf_drowning_sunlight is a combat-
surf map that is made by silverlol.

you will experience fast surf, m3s,
ak47s, colts, snipers, lots of fun
and boosters.

there is room for 84 players

the map was test on Buck Nasty's
surf shack.

-----------------------------------
please report any bugs found, here
or on solidsurf.info. or add me on
steam, m4rk93.

-----------------------------------
i would also like to thank SolidSurf,
ViciousVandals and again, Buck Nasty.

enjoy.
